372
00:25:24,506 --> 00:25:27,276
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu sedikit menakutkan.</font>

373
00:25:27,276 --> 00:25:29,011
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan membingungkan.</font>

374
00:25:29,177 --> 00:25:31,713
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi lebih kasihan orang itu.</font>

375
00:25:31,713 --> 00:25:34,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?/ Jika itu bukan kesalahan mereka,</font>

376
00:25:34,850 --> 00:25:36,418
<font color=#FFFF00>...bukankah kau akan merasa kasihan?</font>

377
00:25:36,818 --> 00:25:39,021
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau hanya perlu menunggu...</font>

378
00:25:39,021 --> 00:25:41,623
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan menunjukkan dukunganmu
sampai keadaan kembali normal.</font>

379
00:25:43,258 --> 00:25:45,427
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, ikut aku.</font>

380
00:25:45,427 --> 00:25:47,262
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka sangat menggemaskan.</font>

381
00:25:50,532 --> 00:25:52,234
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukankah ini keren? Kau mau?</font>

382
00:25:52,234 --> 00:25:55,938
<font color=#FFFF00>Keren apanya. Ini tidak lucu. Ini aneh.</font>

383
00:25:55,938 --> 00:25:59,174
<font color=#FFFF00>Sungguh? Kalau dilihat-lihat,
memang tidak keren.</font>

384
00:25:59,174 --> 00:26:01,343
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi ini menggemaskan.</font>

385
00:26:01,343 --> 00:26:03,779
<font color=#FFFF00>Menggemaskan apanya. Itu kelihatan murahan.</font>

386
00:26:03,779 --> 00:26:04,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak suka.</font>

387
00:26:05,113 --> 00:26:07,482
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga. Kau sangat kasar.</font>

388
00:26:07,549 --> 00:26:11,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Mungkin itu sedikit menggemaskan.</font>

389
00:26:11,520 --> 00:26:12,588
<font color=#FFFF00>Atau mungkin keren?</font>

390
00:26:12,588 --> 00:26:14,456
<font color=#FFFF00>Pikirkan baik-baik.</font>

391
00:26:14,456 --> 00:26:18,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Katakan. Ini keren atau menggemaskan?</font>

392
00:26:22,264 --> 00:26:23,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Keren.</font>

393
00:26:23,498 --> 00:26:24,733
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga.</font>

394
00:26:24,733 --> 00:26:27,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Ambil. Kami akan membeli ini./ Baik.</font>

395
00:26:28,070 --> 00:26:30,973
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan kembali ke rumah sakit
karena piket malam.</font>

396
00:26:30,973 --> 00:26:32,441
<font color=#FFFF00>Bertemanlah dengan dia, oke?</font>

397
00:26:49,791 --> 00:26:51,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Detektif Cha.</font>

398
00:26:54,329 --> 00:26:55,597
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku datang...</font>

399
00:26:56,031 --> 00:26:57,799
<font color=#FFFF00>...untuk mengembalikan ini padamu.</font>

400
00:27:09,511 --> 00:27:11,847
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau Detektif Cha, atau...</font>

401
00:27:11,847 --> 00:27:13,281
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini aku, Dong Tak.</font>

402
00:27:18,820 --> 00:27:21,323
<font color=#FFFF00>Senang bertemu denganmu.</font>

403
00:27:27,696 --> 00:27:29,931
<font color=#FFFF00>Direktur Tak Jung Hwan.</font>

404
00:27:31,299 --> 00:27:34,736
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia berhutang budi apa kepada Ayahku?</font>

405
00:27:36,772 --> 00:27:38,473
<font color=#FFFF00>Satu hal yang pasti,</font>

406
00:27:38,774 --> 00:27:42,210
<font color=#FFFF00>...dia ada kaitannya dengan
kecelakaan mobil Ayahku.</font>

407
00:27:43,245 --> 00:27:46,281
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi kaitan apa itu?</font>

408
00:27:50,986 --> 00:27:52,054
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa itu?</font>

409
00:28:08,804 --> 00:28:10,739
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau baik-baik saja sekarang?</font>

410
00:28:12,074 --> 00:28:13,975
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu sedikit terlambat.</font>

411
00:28:18,080 --> 00:28:19,247
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

412
00:28:20,248 --> 00:28:22,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya aku akan terus kebingungan.</font>

413
00:28:23,185 --> 00:28:25,787
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi setidaknya...</font>

414
00:28:27,222 --> 00:28:28,623
<font color=#FFFF00>...setidaknya,</font>

415
00:28:30,058 --> 00:28:32,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin selalu melihatmu.</font>

416
00:28:33,962 --> 00:28:37,566
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu aku yakin bisa
melihat siapa dirimu.</font>

417
00:28:40,202 --> 00:28:43,371
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak akan takut dan
kabur lagi.</font>

418
00:29:27,716 --> 00:29:28,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar.</font>

419
00:29:29,451 --> 00:29:32,521
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini kasus yang kuceritakan
sebelumnya.</font>

420
00:29:33,088 --> 00:29:34,623
<font color=#FFFF00>Kasus Ayahku.</font>

421
00:29:37,793 --> 00:29:40,162
