425
00:29:55,043 --> 00:29:56,912
<font color=#FFFF00>...Song Ji Seok?</font>

426
00:29:58,513 --> 00:30:00,048
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah Ssong adalah...</font>

427
00:30:00,849 --> 00:30:03,018
<font color=#FFFF00>...Detektif korupsi yang menghancurkan...</font>

428
00:30:03,852 --> 00:30:05,787
<font color=#FFFF00>...bukti Ayahku tidak bersalah?</font>

429
00:30:09,658 --> 00:30:11,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa dia Detektif...</font>

430
00:30:11,960 --> 00:30:14,529
<font color=#FFFF00>...yang bunuh diri saat menyelidiki
